OL,6,Fhas a higher proportion of road
OL,7,Ftraffic casualties than mainland Great
OL,8,FBritain, other British Islands and
OL,9,Fmany European countries.
OL,11,FThat is according to a new report, the
OL,12,FRoad Traffic Collision and Casualty
OL,13,FUpdate, which shows the responded to
OL,14,F932 collisions on the island's roads
OL,15,Fduring 2023.
OL,17,FOf those, 214 casualties were recorded
OL,18,Fwith nearly a quarter killed or
OL,19,Fseriously injured.
