OL,11,FRoad traffic collision figures in 2023:
OL,13,FThe data also found that more
OL,14,Fvulnerable road users were injured in
OL,15,FJersey than in Great Britain.
OL,17,FVulnerable road users are mostly
OL,18,Fdefined as people not in a motor
OL,19,Fvehicle such as pedestrians and
OL,20,Fcyclists but motorcycle riders are
OL,21,Falso included in the group.
