OL,6,FJust under 40% of road casualties in
OL,7,F2022 were vulnerable road users with
OL,8,Fthat figure rising to almost two-
OL,9,Fthirds cumulatively between 2019 and
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FConstable Andy Jehan says the
OL,13,Fstatistics are "very disappointing"
OL,14,Fbut Jersey's road network is very
OL,15,Fdifferent from other countries.
OL,17,FHe explains: "We have a lot of roads
OL,18,Fthat don't have pavements, we have
OL,19,Fvery limited cycling infrastructure.
